title: EU's Barnier: post-Brexit transition "not a given"
text:
EU's Barnier: post-Brexit transition "not a given" Friday, February 09, 2018 - 01:54 
A post-Brexit transition period is ''not a given'', the European Union's Brexit negotiator Michel Barnier warned Britain on Friday, saying London had raised ''substantial'' issues with the plan proposed by the bloc. Ciara Lee reports.
